sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI coding agent
    participant Hook as Agent hook or plugin
    participant Rewrite as rtk rewrite
    participant Perm as permissions
    participant Registry as discover registry
    participant Shell as Shell

    Agent->>Hook: Bash command JSON
    Hook->>Rewrite: rtk rewrite "git status"
    Rewrite->>Perm: check host rules
    Perm-->>Rewrite: Deny, Ask, Allow, or Default
    Rewrite->>Registry: rewrite_command("git status")
    Registry-->>Rewrite: "rtk git status"
    Rewrite-->>Hook: stdout plus exit code
    Hook-->>Agent: updated command or passthrough
    Agent->>Shell: execute command
    Shell-->>Agent: filtered output if RTK was used
